# a mark or symbol worn on the forehead by [[Hindu]]s, ornamentally or as an indication of status
#:*'''2001''': I wore these spots of shine and silver like '''tilaks''', the marks of colour that we Hindus wear on our foreheads as symbols of the divine. — Yann Martel, ''Life of Pi''